{
  "video_id": "6k8YBJ5sgko",
  "title": "How fashion helps us express who we are -- and what we stand for | Kaustav Dey",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12931.0,
      "end_time": 15517.0,
      "text": "I was around 10 when one day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15541.0,
      "end_time": 18284.0,
      "text": "I discovered a box of my father's old things."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18985.0,
      "end_time": 21814.0,
      "text": "In it, under a bunch of his college textbooks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21839.0,
      "end_time": 26311.0,
      "text": "was a pair of black corduroy bell-bottom pants."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27292.0,
      "end_time": 29155.0,
      "text": "These pants were awful --"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29179.0,
      "end_time": 31176.0,
      "text": "musty and moth-eaten."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31200.0,
      "end_time": 33256.0,
      "text": "And of course, I fell in love with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33770.0,
      "end_time": 35395.0,
      "text": "I'd never seen anything like them."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36154.0,
      "end_time": 37623.0,
      "text": "Until that day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37647.0,
      "end_time": 42137.0,
      "text": "all I'd ever known and worn was my school uniform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42161.0,
      "end_time": 45378.0,
      "text": "which, in fact, I was pretty grateful for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45402.0,
      "end_time": 47524.0,
      "text": "because from quite a young age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47548.0,
      "end_time": 50442.0,
      "text": "I'd realized I was somewhat different."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50885.0,
      "end_time": 53245.0,
      "text": "I'd never been one of the boys my age;"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53269.0,
      "end_time": 54771.0,
      "text": "terrible at sports,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54795.0,
      "end_time": 57456.0,
      "text": "possibly the unmanliest little boy ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57480.0,
      "end_time": 58568.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58592.0,
      "end_time": 60257.0,
      "text": "I was bullied quite a bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61408.0,
      "end_time": 66140.0,
      "text": "And so, I figured that to survive I would be invisible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66164.0,
      "end_time": 67749.0,
      "text": "and the uniform helped me"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68532.0,
      "end_time": 71149.0,
      "text": "to seem no different from any other child."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71173.0,
      "end_time": 72350.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72374.0,
      "end_time": 74436.0,
      "text": "Well, almost."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76253.0,
      "end_time": 78240.0,
      "text": "This became my daily prayer:"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78264.0,
      "end_time": 81738.0,
      "text": "\"God, please make me just like everybody else.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83342.0,
      "end_time": 85926.0,
      "text": "I think this went straight to God's voicemail, though."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 85951.0,
      "end_time": 87300.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87270.0,
      "end_time": 89529.0,
      "text": "And eventually, it became pretty clear"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 89553.0,
      "end_time": 93372.0,
      "text": "that I was not growing up to be the son that my father always wanted."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93833.0,
      "end_time": 94983.0,
      "text": "Sorry, Dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97523.0,
      "end_time": 100357.0,
      "text": "No, I was not going to magically change."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100382.0,
      "end_time": 105687.0,
      "text": "And over time, I grew less and less sure that I actually wanted to."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 106740.0,
      "end_time": 111344.0,
      "text": "Therefore, the day those black corduroy bell-bottom pants came into my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111368.0,
      "end_time": 112687.0,
      "text": "something happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113227.0,
      "end_time": 114624.0,
      "text": "I didn't see pants;"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115630.0,
      "end_time": 116564.0,
      "text": "I saw opportunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 117870.0,
      "end_time": 119788.0,
      "text": "The very next day, I had to wear them to school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 119812.0,
      "end_time": 120962.0,
      "text": "come what may."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121820.0,
      "end_time": 125256.0,
      "text": "And once I pulled on those god-awful pants and belted them tight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125844.0,
      "end_time": 130239.0,
      "text": "almost instantly, I developed what can only be called a swagger."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130264.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131896.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 131920.0,
      "end_time": 133585.0,
      "text": "All the way to school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 133610.0,
      "end_time": 136526.0,
      "text": "and then all the way back because I was sent home at once --"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 136550.0,
      "end_time": 137858.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 137882.0,
      "end_time": 141989.0,
      "text": "I transformed into a little brown rock star."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 142130.0,
      "end_time": 143552.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 143576.0,
      "end_time": 146551.0,
      "text": "I finally didn't care anymore that I could not conform."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 146982.0,
      "end_time": 149680.0,
      "text": "That day, I was suddenly celebrating it."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 150770.0,
      "end_time": 153500.0,
      "text": "That day, instead of being invisible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 153524.0,
      "end_time": 155318.0,
      "text": "I chose to be looked at,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 156206.0,
      "end_time": 158279.0,
      "text": "just by wearing something different."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 159136.0,
      "end_time": 163418.0,
      "text": "That day, I discovered the power of what we wear."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 163723.0,
      "end_time": 166396.0,
      "text": "That day, I discovered the power of fashion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 166956.0,
      "end_time": 169250.0,
      "text": "and I've been in love with it ever since."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 170730.0,
      "end_time": 173964.0,
      "text": "Fashion can communicate our differences to the world for us."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 174717.0,
      "end_time": 176754.0,
      "text": "And with this simple act of truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 176778.0,
      "end_time": 179606.0,
      "text": "I realized that these differences --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 179630.0,
      "end_time": 181576.0,
      "text": "they stopped being our shame."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 182413.0,
      "end_time": 185440.0,
      "text": "They became our expressions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 185680.0,
      "end_time": 188472.0,
      "text": "expressions of our very unique identities."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 190138.0,
      "end_time": 192315.0,
      "text": "And we should express ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 192339.0,
      "end_time": 193671.0,
      "text": "wear what we want."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 194285.0,
      "end_time": 196160.0,
      "text": "What's the worst that could happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 196184.0,
      "end_time": 201140.0,
      "text": "The fashion police are going to get you for being so last season?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 201380.0,
      "end_time": 202999.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 204667.0,
      "end_time": 205826.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 206329.0,
      "end_time": 212172.0,
      "text": "Well, unless the fashion police meant something entirely different."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 214880.0,
      "end_time": 218227.0,
      "text": "Nobel Prize laureate Malala survived Taliban extremists"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 218252.0,
      "end_time": 219841.0,
      "text": "in October 2012."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 220495.0,
      "end_time": 225324.0,
      "text": "However, in October 2017, she faced a different enemy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 225906.0,
      "end_time": 229726.0,
      "text": "when online trolls viciously attacked the photograph"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 229750.0,
      "end_time": 232873.0,
      "text": "that showed the 20-year-old wearing jeans that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 233984.0,
      "end_time": 235440.0,
      "text": "The comments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 235464.0,
      "end_time": 236977.0,
      "text": "the hatred she received,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 237100.0,
      "end_time": 239983.0,
      "text": "ranged from \"How long before the scarf comes off?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 240915.0,
      "end_time": 242167.0,
      "text": "to, and I quote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 243800.0,
      "end_time": 246105.0,
      "text": "\"That's the reason the bullet directly targeted her head"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 246129.0,
      "end_time": 247418.0,
      "text": "a long time ago.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 248430.0,
      "end_time": 251880.0,
      "text": "Now, when most of us decide to wear a pair of jeans"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 251112.0,
      "end_time": 254880.0,
      "text": "someplace like New York, London, Milan, Paris,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 256700.0,
      "end_time": 259831.0,
      "text": "we possibly don't stop to think that it's a privilege;"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 261480.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264960.0,
      "text": "something that somewhere else can have consequences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 265429.0,
      "end_time": 268847.0,
      "text": "something that can one day be taken away from us."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 270447.0,
      "end_time": 273541.0,
      "text": "My grandmother was a woman who took extraordinary pleasure"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 273565.0,
      "end_time": 274862.0,
      "text": "in dressing up."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 274886.0,
      "end_time": 276976.0,
      "text": "Her fashion was colorful."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 277000.0,
      "end_time": 280689.0,
      "text": "And the color she loved to wear so much was possibly the only thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 280713.0,
      "end_time": 282617.0,
      "text": "that was truly about her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 282641.0,
      "end_time": 284590.0,
      "text": "the one thing she had agency over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 285139.0,
      "end_time": 287948.0,
      "text": "because like most other women of her generation in India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 287972.0,
      "end_time": 290645.0,
      "text": "she'd never been allowed to exist"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 290670.0,
      "end_time": 293556.0,
      "text": "beyond what was dictated by custom and tradition."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 294535.0,
      "end_time": 296314.0,
      "text": "She'd been married at 17,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 297940.0,
      "end_time": 301784.0,
      "text": "and after 65 years of marriage, when my grandfather died suddenly one day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 303198.0,
      "end_time": 304837.0,
      "text": "her loss was unbearable."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 307122.0,
      "end_time": 310893.0,
      "text": "But that day, she was going to lose something else as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 311514.0,
      "end_time": 312786.0,
      "text": "the one joy she had:"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 313433.0,
      "end_time": 314582.0,
      "text": "to wear color."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 316129.0,
      "end_time": 317983.0,
      "text": "In India, according to custom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 318700.0,
      "end_time": 320283.0,
      "text": "when a Hindu woman becomes a widow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 320307.0,
      "end_time": 323200.0,
      "text": "all she's allowed to wear is white"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 325104.0,
      "text": "from the day of the death of her husband."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 325634.0,
      "end_time": 327771.0,
      "text": "No one made my grandmother wear white."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 328424.0,
      "end_time": 332258.0,
      "text": "However, every woman she'd known who had outlived her husband,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 332283.0,
      "end_time": 333866.0,
      "text": "including her mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 333890.0,
      "end_time": 335390.0,
      "text": "had done it."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 335463.0,
      "end_time": 339847.0,
      "text": "This oppression was so internalized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 339871.0,
      "end_time": 341467.0,
      "text": "so deep-rooted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 341492.0,
      "end_time": 344135.0,
      "text": "that she herself refused a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 346649.0,
      "end_time": 348541.0,
      "text": "She passed away this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 348565.0,
      "end_time": 350167.0,
      "text": "and until the day she died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 350191.0,
      "end_time": 352342.0,
      "text": "she continued to wear only white."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 356275.0,
      "end_time": 359741.0,
      "text": "I have a photograph with her from earlier, happier times."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 360376.0,
      "end_time": 363390.0,
      "text": "In it, you can't really see what she's wearing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 363415.0,
      "end_time": 365205.0,
      "text": "the photo is in black and white."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 365783.0,
      "end_time": 368615.0,
      "text": "However, from the way she's smiling in it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 368639.0,
      "end_time": 370525.0,
      "text": "you just know she's wearing color."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 372382.0,
      "end_time": 375235.0,
      "text": "This is also what fashion can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 375259.0,
      "end_time": 377374.0,
      "text": "It has the power to fill us with joy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 377836.0,
      "end_time": 383116.0,
      "text": "the joy of freedom to choose for ourselves how we want to look,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 383140.0,
      "end_time": 384668.0,
      "text": "how we want to live --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 385638.0,
      "end_time": 387955.0,
      "text": "a freedom worth fighting for."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 388608.0,
      "end_time": 392593.0,
      "text": "And fighting for freedom, protest, comes in many forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 393805.0,
      "end_time": 396975.0,
      "text": "Widows in India like my grandmother, thousands of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 396999.0,
      "end_time": 398853.0,
      "text": "live in a city called Vrindavan."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 399720.0,
      "end_time": 402675.0,
      "text": "And so, it's been a sea of white for centuries."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 404608.0,
      "end_time": 407702.0,
      "text": "However, only as recently as 2013,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 407726.0,
      "end_time": 411456.0,
      "text": "the widows of Vrindavan have started to celebrate Holi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 411947.0,
      "end_time": 413957.0,
      "text": "the Indian festival of color,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 414665.0,
      "end_time": 416934.0,
      "text": "which they are prohibited from participating in."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 418615.0,
      "end_time": 420235.0,
      "text": "On this one day in March,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 420259.0,
      "end_time": 423962.0,
      "text": "these women take the traditional colored powder of the festival"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 424705.0,
      "end_time": 426178.0,
      "text": "and color each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 427454.0,
      "end_time": 431383.0,
      "text": "With every handful of the powder they throw into the air,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 431407.0,
      "end_time": 435241.0,
      "text": "their white saris slowly start to suffuse with color."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 436423.0,
      "end_time": 439867.0,
      "text": "And they don't stop until they're completely covered"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 439891.0,
      "end_time": 443524.0,
      "text": "in every hue of the rainbow that's forbidden to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 444889.0,
      "end_time": 446772.0,
      "text": "The color washes off the next day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 447395.0,
      "end_time": 450457.0,
      "text": "however, for that moment in time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 450482.0,
      "end_time": 452756.0,
      "text": "it's their beautiful disruption."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 454742.0,
      "end_time": 456132.0,
      "text": "This disruption,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 457820.0,
      "end_time": 458561.0,
      "text": "any kind of dissonance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 459116.0,
      "end_time": 463113.0,
      "text": "can be the first gauntlet we throw down in a battle against oppression."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 464279.0,
      "end_time": 465465.0,
      "text": "And fashion --"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 465926.0,
      "end_time": 468336.0,
      "text": "it can create visual disruption for us --"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 468926.0,
      "end_time": 470316.0,
      "text": "on us, literally."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 471942.0,
      "end_time": 474521.0,
      "text": "Lessons of defiance have always been taught"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 474545.0,
      "end_time": 476518.0,
      "text": "by fashion's great revolutionaries:"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 477450.0,
      "end_time": 478226.0,
      "text": "its designers."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 479410.0,
      "end_time": 483985.0,
      "text": "Jean Paul Gaultier taught us that women can be kings."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 484718.0,
      "end_time": 486650.0,
      "text": "Thom Browne --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 486890.0,
      "end_time": 488906.0,
      "text": "he taught us that men can wear heels."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 490392.0,
      "end_time": 494847.0,
      "text": "And Alexander McQueen, in his spring 1999 show,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 494871.0,
      "end_time": 497912.0,
      "text": "had two giant robotic arms in the middle of his runway."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 499222.0,
      "end_time": 504114.0,
      "text": "And as the model, Shalom Harlow began to spin in between them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 504139.0,
      "end_time": 506268.0,
      "text": "these two giant arms --"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 506292.0,
      "end_time": 508772.0,
      "text": "furtively at first and then furiously,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 508796.0,
      "end_time": 510897.0,
      "text": "began to spray color onto her."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 511328.0,
      "end_time": 513690.0,
      "text": "McQueen, thus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 513690.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515414.00000000006,
      "text": "before he took his own life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 515438.0,
      "end_time": 519429.0,
      "text": "taught us that this body of ours is a canvas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 520870.0,
      "end_time": 524780.0,
      "text": "a canvas we get to paint however we want."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 525467.0,
      "end_time": 527697.0,
      "text": "Somebody who loved this world of fashion"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 527721.0,
      "end_time": 529187.0,
      "text": "was Karar Nushi."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 529548.0,
      "end_time": 531640.0,
      "text": "He was a student and actor from Iraq."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 532348.0,
      "end_time": 534693.0,
      "text": "He loved his vibrant, eclectic clothes."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 535164.0,
      "end_time": 539983.0,
      "text": "However, he soon started receiving death threats for how he looked."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 540764.0,
      "end_time": 542195.0,
      "text": "He remained unfazed."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 542754.0,
      "end_time": 544602.0,
      "text": "He remained fabulous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 544626.0,
      "end_time": 546593.0,
      "text": "until July 2017,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 546618.0,
      "end_time": 550660.0,
      "text": "when Karar was discovered dead on a busy street in Baghdad."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 553910.0,
      "end_time": 555433.0,
      "text": "He'd been kidnapped."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 556480.0,
      "end_time": 557741.0,
      "text": "He'd been tortured."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 558701.0,
      "end_time": 562909.0,
      "text": "And eyewitnesses say that his body showed multiple wounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 564190.0,
      "end_time": 565197.0,
      "text": "Stab wounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 567838.0,
      "end_time": 570117.0,
      "text": "Two thousand miles away in Peshawar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 570141.0,
      "end_time": 576553.0,
      "text": "Pakistani transgender activist Alisha was shot multiple times in May 2016."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 577339.0,
      "end_time": 579375.0,
      "text": "She was taken to the hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 579399.0,
      "end_time": 581574.0,
      "text": "but because she dressed in women's clothing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 581598.0,
      "end_time": 585949.0,
      "text": "she was refused access to either the men's or the women's wards."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 588270.0,
      "end_time": 592473.0,
      "text": "What we choose to wear can sometimes be literally life and death."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 593569.0,
      "end_time": 596660.0,
      "text": "And even in death, we sometimes don't get to choose."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 597387.0,
      "end_time": 598991.0,
      "text": "Alisha died that day"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 599150.0,
      "end_time": 601380.0,
      "text": "and then was buried as a man."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 602753.0,
      "end_time": 604378.0,
      "text": "What kind of world is this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 605142.0,
      "end_time": 608714.0,
      "text": "Well, it's one in which it's natural to be afraid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 609856.0,
      "end_time": 612388.0,
      "text": "to be frightened of this surveillance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 612412.0,
      "end_time": 615731.0,
      "text": "this violence against our bodies and what we wear on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 616928.0,
      "end_time": 621624.0,
      "text": "However, the greater fear is that once we surrender,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 621648.0,
      "end_time": 622821.0,
      "text": "blend in"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 622845.0,
      "end_time": 625210.0,
      "text": "and begin to disappear one after the other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 625907.0,
      "end_time": 628644.0,
      "text": "the more normal this false conformity will look,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 629693.0,
      "end_time": 631997.0,
      "text": "the less shocking this oppression will feel."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 634285.0,
      "end_time": 635920.0,
      "text": "For the children we are raising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 636840.0,
      "end_time": 640957.0,
      "text": "the injustice of today could become the ordinary of tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 642849.0,
      "end_time": 644296.0,
      "text": "They'll get used to this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 645104.0,
      "end_time": 648858.0,
      "text": "and they, too, might begin to see anything different as dirty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 650413.0,
      "end_time": 651791.0,
      "text": "something to be hated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 652763.0,
      "end_time": 654476.0,
      "text": "something to be extinguished,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 655546.0,
      "end_time": 657123.0,
      "text": "like lights to be put out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 657147.0,
      "end_time": 658314.0,
      "text": "one by one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 658338.0,
      "end_time": 660344.0,
      "text": "until darkness becomes a way of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 662738.0,
      "end_time": 664924.0,
      "text": "However, if I today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 664948.0,
      "end_time": 666405.0,
      "text": "then you tomorrow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 666429.0,
      "end_time": 668274.0,
      "text": "maybe even more of us someday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 668298.0,
      "end_time": 671161.0,
      "text": "if we embrace our right to look like ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 671185.0,
      "end_time": 674740.0,
      "text": "then in the world that's been violently whitewashed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 674990.0,
      "end_time": 676772.0,
      "text": "we will become the pinpricks of color pushing through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 677286.0,
      "end_time": 679184.0,
      "text": "much like those widows of Vrindavan."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 681930.0,
      "end_time": 684536.0,
      "text": "How then, with so many of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 684561.0,
      "end_time": 686641.0,
      "text": "will the crosshairs of a gun"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 686665.0,
      "end_time": 688567.0,
      "text": "be able to pick out Karar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 689412.0,
      "end_time": 690567.0,
      "text": "Malala,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 691480.0,
      "end_time": 692203.0,
      "text": "Alisha?"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 694223.0,
      "end_time": 695521.0,
      "text": "Can they kill us all?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 698533.0,
      "end_time": 700306.0,
      "text": "The time is now to stand up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 701171.0,
      "end_time": 702539.0,
      "text": "to stand out."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 703407.0,
      "end_time": 705782.0,
      "text": "Where sameness is safeness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 705806.0,
      "end_time": 708331.0,
      "text": "with something as simple as what we wear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 708355.0,
      "end_time": 710567.0,
      "text": "we can draw every eye to ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 711410.0,
      "end_time": 715427.0,
      "text": "to say that there are differences in this world, and there always will be."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 716183.0,
      "end_time": 717417.0,
      "text": "Get used to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 718511.0,
      "end_time": 721430.0,
      "text": "And this we can say without a single word."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 721844.0,
      "end_time": 724798.0,
      "text": "Fashion can give us a language for dissent."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 725710.0,
      "end_time": 727208.0,
      "text": "It can give us courage."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 727971.0,
      "end_time": 732258.0,
      "text": "Fashion can let us literally wear our courage on our sleeves."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 733644.0,
      "end_time": 734797.0,
      "text": "So wear it."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 736327.0,
      "end_time": 737808.0,
      "text": "Wear it like armor."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 738771.0,
      "end_time": 740468.0,
      "text": "Wear it because it matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 741530.0,
      "end_time": 743700.0,
      "text": "And wear it because you matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 743817.0,
      "end_time": 744967.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 744991.0,
      "end_time": 748161.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}